      "text": "azure-pipelines.yml is the “job definition” for Azure DevOps: when to run, what agent pool to use,\nand which scripts to execute (build/test/scan/publish/stage).",
      "fontSize": 2.5023505106356136,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "azure-pipelines.yml is the “job definition” for Azure DevOps: when to run, what agent pool to use, and which scripts to execute (build/test/scan/publish/stage).",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "5uRXx3iP5DhkOkoBywCgb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 19701.78679013154,
      "y": 1277.8262707944257,
      "width": 112.88500690197812,
      "height": 9.38381441488355,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bJI",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1387660655,
      "version": 918,
      "versionNonce": 1870907841,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776079836775,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Alternatives to Azure Pipelines\nGitHub Actions, Jenkins, TeamCity, GitLab CI, CircleCI, etc. Same concept: YAML defines steps;\nscripts do the work.",
      "fontSize": 2.5023505106356136,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Alternatives to Azure Pipelines\nGitHub Actions, Jenkins, TeamCity, GitLab CI, CircleCI, etc. Same concept: YAML defines steps; scripts do the work.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "DpfnmIBsRQAVxwhMGmBgc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 19886.17181370049,
      "y": 785.8909197044729,
      "width": 90.59102033231865,
      "height": 18.146481700545223,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bJJ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 757675471,
      "version": 1196,
      "versionNonce": 1878254593,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776079724306,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Today, mcp.json is optimized for a developer machine because it runs:\ndotnet run --project <path-to-csproj>\nFor a deployable exe, we’d typically:\nbuild/publish once (producing an .exe), then\npoint mcp.json at the exe instead of dotnet run.",
      "fontSize": 2.9034370720872356,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Today, mcp.json is optimized for a developer machine because it runs:\ndotnet run --project <path-to-csproj>\nFor a deployable exe, we’d typically:\nbuild/publish once (producing an .exe), then\npoint mcp.json at the exe instead of dotnet run.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
