      "updated": 1776079876239,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The purpose of a CODEOWNERS file (like .github/CODEOWNERS) is to tell GitHub “who is responsible for which parts of the repo”.",
      "fontSize": 3.586758010326511,
      "fontFamily": 6,
